      • initiateStream

        public AsyncResult<ByteStreamSession> initiateStream​(Jid receiver,
                                                     SIFileTransferOffer profile,
                                                     String mimeType,
                                                     Duration timeout)
        Initiates a stream with another entity.
        Parameters:
        receiver - The receiver, i.e. the XMPP entity you want to negotiate a stream.
        profile - The profile. Currently there's only the SIFileTransferOffer profile.
        mimeType - The mime type of the stream.
        timeout - The timeout, which wait until the stream has been negotiated.
        Returns:
        The async result with the output stream which has been negotiated.
